- VSCode Version: Code 1.7.1 (02611b40b24c9df2726ad8b33f5ef5f67ac30b44, 2016-11-03T13:53:14.822Z)
- OS Version: Windows_NT ia32 10.0.14393


Steps to Reproduce:

1. use the following scss

```
    tr {
        th, td { 
            border-bottom: 1px solid gray;
            @at-root #{selector-replace(&, "tr", "tr:last-child")} {
                border-bottom: 0;
            }
        }
    }
```

2. It is valid SCSS, but is it mark as an error. Using `#{&}` instead, does works.
